<!-- ABOUT -->

  <script type="text/x-handlebars" id="about">
    <h2>About<img src="images/embermmblack.svg"></h2>
    <div class="abouttext">
      <p>Hello!</p>
      <p>EmberMM is an opensource personal project.</p>
      <p>I made this to serve as a boilerplate for Middleman using EmberJS and Bootstrap to help streamline the development process and make it easier to start a project. I have used The CSS3 Animation Cheatsheet from Justin Aguilar to easily add animations without needing much or any jQuery experience. I also added some custom SCSS variables in plain english to help easily customize bootstrap without the headache of searching for classnames. Mark Allen was nice enough to contribute a (simple) but extremely efficient way of safely console logging your JS/jQuery code without having to worry about crashing Internet Explorer.</p>
      <p>If you can or want to use this, Feel free!</p>
      <p> -Danny Vassallo</p>
    </div>

  </script>

